<% content_for :exhibition do %>
  <div class="articleContainer">
    <div class="spacer">
      <div class="description">
        <article>
          <h1>What is <%= image_tag 'projectlodge-light.png', :alt => '.projectlodge',:class => 'projectlodgeLogo' %>?</h1>
          <div class="column">
            <p>The question should not be what, but who! Linking people together in an open and free environment to do what they like to do. Create musical instruments, collaborate on art pieces, helping out a local causes, plan performances and anything you can imagine. Innovating together in technology and growing personally in knowledge.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <p>We as .projectlodge ARE the platform on wich we do innovative, technological and fun projects. Together on Local and Global level. We find each other and collaborate on the future!</p>
            <p>We want to enable the individual to contribute to the world on their own terms, level and field.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
      <%= render :partial => 'layouts/authentication_widget' %>
      <div class="break"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>
<div class="row">
  <div class="column col2-3">
    <div class="gridSpacer">
      <div class="newsRotator">
        <header>
          <h2>Latest news from the community.</h2>
        </header>
        <div class="block">
          <div class="article blockSpacer">
            <article>
              <div class="container">
                <h1>BAM2011S announced</h1>
                <p>Today the next Bi-Annual meeting is announced. Read more on the <%= link_to 'meeting page', '/bam2011s' %></p>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
          <div class="article blockSpacer">
            <article>
              <div class="container">
                <h1>The BETA site is live!</h1>
                <p>Today we launched the first beta version of the projectlodge.org website.</p>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
          <div class="article blockSpacer">
            <article>
              <div class="container">
                <h1>Founding of the association</h1>
                <p>Our plan is to start the organization as a association (Dutch: vereniging).</p>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="column col1-3">
    <div class="gridSpacer block twitterBlock" id="organization_twitter">
      <h4><%= link_to '.projectlodge on twitter', 'http://twitter.com/projectlodge' %></h4>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script>
    $(function () {
      $('#organization_twitter').railcoachTwitterWidget();
    });
  </script>
</div>
